---
// Apply CTA — full-bleed bottom-of-page conversion catch
---

<section class="py-32 sm:py-40 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center opacity-30"
    style="background-image:url('/cta/apply-bg.jpg');"
  >
  </div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-darker via-brand-dark/95 to-brand-darker"></div>
  <div
    class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[700px] h-[700px] bg-brand-gold/[0.06] rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 text-center">
    <span
      class="text-brand-gold text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6 block"
    >
      The Door Is Open
    </span>
    <h2
      class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-display font-black uppercase tracking-tighter mb-8 leading-[0.9]"
    >
      Step Up. <span class="text-brand-gold">Get Represented.</span>
    </h2>
    <p
      class="text-base sm:text-lg text-white/70 font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed"
    >
      MMA. Kun Khmer. Grappling. If you're built for it, we'll get you on the
      card. Apply for representation — five minutes, three disciplines, one
      shot at the world stage.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="/apply"
        class="group bg-brand-gold text-black px-12 py-5 font-bold rounded-xl text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] hover:bg-white transition-all shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(212,175,55,0.3)] active:scale-95 flex items-center gap-3"
      >
        Apply Now
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          width="16"
          height="16"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2.5"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
          ><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"></path></svg
        >
      </a>
      <a
        href="/partner"
        class="px-12 py-5 font-bold rounded-xl text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] border border-white/15 text-white/80 hover:text-white hover:border-white/30 hover:bg-white/5 transition-all active:scale-95"
      >
        Partner with Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
